-> nums1[i] + nums2[j] = - ( nums3[k] + nums4[l])

# Approach
We get all Combinations of nums1 and nums2 into a map 
and then traverse into combinations of nums3 and nums4 and check for 
-( nums[k] + nums[l]) in the map

# Complexity
